{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Finance Data Processing & Access Control API","description":"A finance dashboard backend supporting:\n- JWT authentication\n- Role-based access control (VIEWER / ANALYST / ADMIN)\n- Financial record management (CRUD + filtering)\n- Dashboard analytics (totals, trends, category breakdown)\n\n**Default credentials:**\n| Username | Password | Role |\n|---|---|---|\n| admin | admin123 | ADMIN |\n| analyst | analyst123 | ANALYST |\n| viewer | viewer123 | VIEWER |\n\nLogin via `POST /api/auth/login`, copy the token, click **Authorize** and enter `Bearer <token>`.\n","contact":{"name":"FDPACB","email":"admin@fdpacb.dev"},"version":"1.0.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:8080","description":"Generated server url"}],"security":[{"bearerAuth":[]}],"tags":[{"name":"Authentication","description":"Register and login endpoints"},{"name":"Financial Records","description":"CRUD and filtering for financial transactions"},{"name":"User Management","description":"ADMIN-only user management operations"},{"name":"Dashboard","description":"Analytics and summary endpoints"}],"paths":{"/api/users/{id}":{"get":{"tags":["User Management"],"summary":"Get user by ID [ADMIN]","operationId":"getUserById","parameters":[{"name":"id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","format":"uuid"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UserResponse"}}}}},"security":[{"bearerAuth":[]}]},"put":{"tags":["User Management"],"summary":"Update user role or status [ADMIN]","operationId":"updateUser","parameters":[{"name":"id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","format":"uuid"}}],"requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UpdateUserRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UserResponse"}}}}},"security":[{"bearerAuth":[]}]},"delete":{"tags":["User Management"],"s